{"tid":211391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又有勇者測試------------繼續恥笑！KFC點餐機！","createTime":"2017-04-21T15:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T17:17:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df019915b624fe470724060b10bbb7bbf1233969","tid":211391,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:09:52.000Z","msg":"相信有食開老麥的人都不會對自助點餐機陌生，不過今次KFC推出的「KFC 快趣點餐機」就特別啦！超越對手的自助點餐機，擁有全球獨有的「粵語語音識別系統」之餘，又可以偵測手部動作！不過不經過實試又怎知有沒有誇大其方便性呢～　娜姐（和張繼聰）就身先士卒啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/kfc-article-694x390.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fkfc-article-694x390.png&h=4de4f43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想食雞就要大聲講</span><br />\n<br />\nKFC投資逾500萬，開發了6個月的「KFC快趣點餐機」搶先在金鐘海富中心分店推出，而點餐機一大賣點就是可以隔空點餐，只要你出句聲就得，而且更聽得懂廣東話！但於開幕當日（4月20日），張繼聰為大家實試時就出現尷尬場面了&hellip;似乎點餐機的粵語語音識別系統未太熟廣東話呢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開發期間，團隊都有考慮到餐廳環境會有些嘈雜，所以點餐機的收音系統選擇採用載有Creative CrystalVoice&trade;立體聲陣列式麥克風，有效隔音及集中收音的作用。而娜姐使用時都覺得即使周圍很多人，都可以清楚聽到點餐機的聲音；至於落單要落得快而準，就要注意咬字啦！當日更有工作人員指，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點餐機需要時間去學習識別不同人的聲線以及說話習慣</span>。（不過老實講，要重覆太多次都有點不耐煩&hellip;）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/04/21/kfcorder-selfhelpmachine-chicken/hottopic/lifestyle-review/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F04%2F21%2Fkfcorder-selfhelpmachine-chicken%2Fhottopic%2Flifestyle-review%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5943ae17\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/04/21/kfcorder-selfhelpmachine-chicken/hottopic/lifestyle-review/</a>"},{"pid":"95b8282921acb62f730f5a256fcb6de81ea96cd0","tid":211391,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點餐機需要時間去學習識別不同人的聲線以及說話習慣</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9133039b8c3a7141eb3be947557421e5f2fef21b","tid":211391,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:11:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想食雞就要大聲講<br />\n想食雞就要大聲講<br />\n想食雞就要大聲講<br />\n想食雞就要大聲講<br />\n想食雞就要大聲講</span>"},{"pid":"4d9466e5dd933929eb34ae4ff1192ac44c650b92","tid":211391,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"有冇遊b新圖"},{"pid":"1263a22629d3b5672ecf8440b21744a80c8968ba","tid":211391,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93a7e624ce37988b5913411ebfaf7d8ef4d6a71f","tid":211391,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇遊b新圖</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Y6SO8i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Y6SO8i.jpg&h=f1959f03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7672219271851b0b194f33faabb13c50e2235c0b","tid":211391,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddfaac1d9d099ae8455d748ff2ecbcb3178ba91","tid":211391,"uid":18566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"你個野壞左呀"},{"pid":"497a55ab84793368a899289898287496825a6103","tid":211391,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T15:26:02.000Z","msg":"好心淨係整個app 就算喇 整果部機真係攞黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1806039848facf17d52